@startuml
[*] --> Unbound
Unbound --> GymBoundToClass : teacher selects gym
GymBoundToClass --> CatalogSyncDue : worker sees teacher credential
CatalogSyncDue --> CatalogSynced : owned gym list fetched
CatalogSynced --> StandingDue : bound gym needs projection refresh
StandingDue --> SyncingStanding : worker calls standings API
SyncingStanding --> StandingSynced : problems and rows persisted
SyncingStanding --> RetryLater : API error/timeout
RetryLater --> StandingDue : next job loop
StandingSynced --> StandingDue : next interval
GymBoundToClass --> Unbound : teacher unbinds gym
@enduml
